{"tid":385823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人因為空氣太差所以出事","createTime":"2017-09-03T13:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T17:30:46.000Z","uid":79353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55f65a7ce9f4a9a35adda6e94143ddc9601c999b","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"醫畜我愛你<br />\n開左隻氣管舒張藥<br />\n細個有哮喘噴過, 已經完全唔同左<br />\n同埋轉介去睇下個肺<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1edf139f281bcb7324167c8594ecfe0a940208a4","tid":385823,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"樓主可以識個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a377dcaceae3df87125722a668b5bcb96c9fad79","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"可能真係空氣太差<br />\n尤其呢排打風打夕<br />\n感覺透唔到氣<br />\n唔識點講<br />\n係外面等巴士，唔係等得好耐，但覺得點呼吸都吸唔夠氣咁<br />\n唔識講<br />\n懷疑係氣管問題，少少哮喘之類，所以俾隻藥需要時試噴，睇下有冇用<br />\n<br />\n最近有點心律不正<br />\n訓訓下覺突然間有一下心跳慢到停左，之後成個人醒返晒..."},{"pid":"fa790fb28011286bbcc0321b96a857b18230e35e","tid":385823,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"淨係知我個鼻被紙巾擦損哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626fa649887e7b61a58844240b74dd1183421f59","tid":385823,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"腎差"},{"pid":"0f627a69e83c90430de13435e927da636d566eff","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係知我個鼻被紙巾擦損哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個鼻又冇乜特別事發生<br />\n<br />\n係成個人身體好差"},{"pid":"91d069ee5b567267b1f47f1d95b3725080d20662","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腎差</blockquote><br />\n唔知呀唉<br />\n<br />\n比起D人日日食韓式炸雞<br />\n<br />\n我已經算清淡 好似係"},{"pid":"7f59d22efd9b29e9bc31a61dfe48cec2d5f8c542","tid":385823,"uid":130789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"有 好辛苦"},{"pid":"82016795505058a4210152874f5feafb687d93e3","tid":385823,"uid":119834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"我細個都有哮喘 呢幾日就算係屋企 條氣都係好唔順<br />\n好似就黎想發作咁"},{"pid":"372a4688eb305831624f23da18861b763c0529cd","tid":385823,"uid":130789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"我一直鼻敏感 <br />\n呢幾日明明鼻係通<br />\n但就成日都透大氣 同埋狂咳 特別夜晚<br />\n想問咁係咪氣管問題？"},{"pid":"e0ecd369d55e5d5aef358bebc4cfb12815c8fdc0","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細個都有哮喘 呢幾日就算係屋企 條氣都係好唔順<br />\n好似就黎想發作咁</blockquote><br />\n我好細個有<br />\n大個唔知點解突然冇左<br />\n<br />\n可能呢排真係空氣太差<br />\n好想個夏天快D過<br />\n再係咁落去唔知有冇命捱到12月<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n呢排朝早/中午出去等一陣車，已經唔係等得耐，條氣好唔順咁，唔知點解<br />\n之後再上一上樓梯，行得急少少，開始個人意識迷糊，即刻去急症順便檢查下<br />\n但次次都係做果Ｄ野，心電圖、心肺Ｘ光、驗血，次次都話冇事<br />\n<br />\n今次醫生算好肯寫紙轉介去睇下個肺<br />\n同埋俾左氣管舒張劑我<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n個夏天可唔可以快D過<br />\n唔明點解想身體健康都咁難<br />\n<br />\n話時話以前減肥PO見過有哮喘病人想室外跑步<br />\n個PO都過左好耐<br />\n我有D擔心佢，而家香港空氣太差，差到我十世冇哮喘過，但成個呼吸系統都好辛苦，希望佢唔好有事"},{"pid":"946143bedd7ac5c89e7837c056fde42dbfb6ba5d","tid":385823,"uid":47645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"而家空氣指數正常返"},{"pid":"59daec8d4f770bf3e86cc72a11562a46e8cb28c4","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一直鼻敏感 <br />\n呢幾日明明鼻係通<br />\n但就成日都透大氣 同埋狂咳 特別夜晚<br />\n想問咁係咪氣管問題？</blockquote><br />\n我今日急症室等，好快到我<br />\n<br />\n如果你去急症室話乜野狂咳、心口痛、透唔到氣之類，<br />\n多數心電圖＋心肺Ｘ光＋抽血檢查<br />\n<br />\n因為我好多次暈／成個人唔舒服都係咁，<br />\n其實冇乜特別檢查可以做到<br />\n<br />\n除非自己出去私家睇<br />\n或者醫院肯轉介去公立專科"},{"pid":"d69d56e39db60a06454db570c927025dcc408948","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家空氣指數正常返</blockquote><br />\n呢排訓覺都心律不正，臨訓著果一下，心跳突然間慢到停左一下，成個人即刻醒返<br />\n如果邊日我突然間死左真係唔出奇"},{"pid":"3a2334f2d8e64cc8da6ae52991caad396c8d0fb3","tid":385823,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"而家真係覺得訓著左未必有機會醒返<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁講好似誇張左<br />\n<br />\n不過今日係分流站同護士講野<br />\n<br />\n成個人真係冇晒氣<br />\n<br />\n而我只不過係少少唔夠訓+行左兩層樓梯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca95ffdeffce964e45d012cdd4be0432b3c26fd","tid":385823,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"想夏天快d過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不嬲冬天空氣先係最差"},{"pid":"e6b3fb09658c83a0e8b35a882e5260ddc282c55d","tid":385823,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家空氣指數正常返</blockquote><br />\n星期五六差到仆街，有毒霧"},{"pid":"2db063a6bf445b350e669027079d35b0756f89e4","tid":385823,"uid":141563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"早兩日睇返廿年前既鏗鏘集  個情況好相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=-SYZNRAispM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-SYZNRAispM&d=RKd7FSYzb7Hpi5FCrb8KuqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fb09ae7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=-SYZNRAispM</a>"},{"pid":"46e84bfd3251ce2c73a303978e17749c7a39fc8f","tid":385823,"uid":130789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早兩日睇返廿年前既鏗鏘集  個情況好相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=-SYZNRAispM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-SYZNRAispM&d=RKd7FSYzb7Hpi5FCrb8KuqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fb09ae7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=-SYZNRAispM</a></blockquote><br />\n但我踢波果陣又乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係平時出街就透大氣"}]}